---
import { getAllCategories } from "../../data/products";

const categories = getAllCategories();
---


<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-300">
  <div class="container max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div>
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <img src="/logos/logo-pcatracha-sinfondo.png" alt="La Pulpería Catracha" class="h-10 w-10 object-contain brightness-0 invert" />
          <span class="font-bold text-lg text-white">Pulpería <span class="text-primary">Catracha</span></span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Tu pulpería de confianza, 100% Catracha. Traemos lo mejor de Honduras directamente a tu mesa, con la calidez y el sabor que nos caracteriza.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <a href="#" class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg border border-gray-600 flex items-center justify-center hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors" aria-label="Facebook">
            <i class="ti ti-brand-facebook"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg border border-gray-600 flex items-center justify-center hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors" aria-label="Instagram">
            <i class="ti ti-brand-instagram"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg border border-gray-600 flex items-center justify-center hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors" aria-label="WhatsApp">
            <i class="ti ti-brand-whatsapp"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h6 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4">Categorías</h6>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm">
          {categories.map((cat) => (
            <li><a href={`/tienda/${cat.slug}`} class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">{cat.name}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h6 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4">Atención al Cliente</h6>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm">
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Sobre Nosotros</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Preguntas Frecuentes</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Política de Envíos</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Términos y Condiciones</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Contáctanos</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h6 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4">Contácto</h6>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="ti ti-map-pin text-primary mt-0.5"></i>
            <span>2644 S 144TH ST<br />Seatac WA 98168<br />Unit B</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="ti ti-phone text-primary mt-0.5"></i>
            <span>(206) 306-5745</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="ti ti-mail text-primary mt-0.5"></i>
            <span>info@pulperiacatracha.hn</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="ti ti-clock text-primary mt-0.5"></i>
            <span>Lun–Sáb: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-gray-800">
    <div class="container max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-5">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} La Pulpería Catracha. Todos los derechos reservados.</span>
        <span>Hecho con <span class="text-primary">♥</span> en Honduras</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
